Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Glupe* ideje su mučile njegov um. (Stupid ideas were troubling his mind.)
2. Ona je tako *glupa*, nije mogla da reši jednostavan zadatak. (She is so stupid, she couldn't solve a simple task.)
3. *Glupe* izjave političara često izazivaju kontroverze. (Stupid statements by politicians often cause controversies.)
4. Čini mi se da je ova knjiga prilično *glupa*. (I think this book is quite stupid.)
5. Ne možeš da veruješ koliko je neko *glup* dok ga ne upoznaš. (You can't believe how stupid someone is until you meet them.)
6. Uvek me iznenadi koliko *glupo* mogu da se ponašaju ljudi na internetu. (I'm always surprised by how stupid people can behave on the internet.)
7. Njegov *glupi* smeh iritirao je sve u sobi. (His stupid laughter annoyed everyone in the room.)
8. Dečko je bio toliko *glup* da je pao na najjednostavnijem testu. (The boy was so stupid that he failed the easiest test.)
9. To je bila najgora odluka koju sam ikada doneo, tako *glupa*. (That was the worst decision I've ever made, so stupid.)
10. Ponekad se osećam kao da sam ja jedini koji ne prati *glupu* modu. (Sometimes I feel like I'm the only one who doesn't follow stupid fashion.)